               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> Was it you gave information about the prisoner A It was—I never stole any leather, or took any to make shoes of—I made a shoulder-strap of a piece of leather—this piece is of no value but to a coach-maker—my master does not permit us to take any, but it is a thing that is generally done—I have seen both of my shop-mates do it,</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
